     "data": {

       "3"

     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def find_count(my_array, element):\n",
    "      \n",
    "    # store the count\n",
    "    count=0\n",
    "        \n",
    "    # iterate each element\n",
    "    # and count the occurrences\n",
    "    # of the specified element\n",
    "    for i in my_array:\n",
    "        if i != element:\n",
    "            count = count + 1\n",
    "            \n",
    "    return(count) \n",
    "# test for def find count for season 2012 to 2014\n",
    "a = '2012'\n",
    "b = '2014'\n",
    "begin = Sdict[a]\n",
    "end = 1 + Sdict [b]\n",
    "x = Seasons[begin:end]\n",
    "scount = find_count(x,'2014') + 1\n",
    "#works\n",
    "scount\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 45,
   "id": "3fb6851e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 576x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "dark"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def find_count(my_array, element):\n",
    "      \n",
    "    # store the count\n",
    "    count=0\n",
    "        \n",
    "    # iterate each element\n",
    "    # and count the occurrences\n",
    "    # of the specified element\n",
    "    for i in my_array:\n",
    "        if i != element:\n",
    "            count = count + 1\n",
    "            \n",
    "    return(count) \n",
    "#prompt for timeframe\n",
    "#a = input(\"Starting Year \")\n",
    "#b = input(\"Ending Year \")\n",
    "a = '2005'\n",
    "b = '2014'\n",
    "begin = Sdict[a]\n",
    "end = 1 + Sdict[b]\n",
    "x = Seasons[begin:end]\n",
    "#count of seasons to observe\n",
    "scount = find_count(x,'2014') + 1\n",
    "#tested def find_count for returning specificed years of observations\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.plot(Games[0][begin:end], c='Black', ls='--', marker='s', ms=7, label=Players[0])\n",
    "plt.plot(Games[1][begin:end], c='Red', ls='--', marker='o', ms=7, label=Players[1])\n",
    "plt.plot(Games[9][begin:end], c='Magenta', ls='--', marker='o', ms=7, label=Players[9])\n",
    "plt.legend(loc = 'upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))\n",
    "plt.xticks(list(range(scount)), Seasons[begin:end])\n",
    "# rotation = 'vertical'\n",
    "# used for xticks or yticks to rotate text\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"Year\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"Games\", rotation = 'horizontal',labelpad = 30 )\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "#Could use counter to replace # def_find_count\n",
    "#counter = Sdict[b]+1 - Sdict[a]\n",
    "#counter\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 46,
   "id": "30bfffc3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "title = 'title'\n",
    "def myplot(playerlist):\n",
    "    #title of chart\n",
    "    #title = input(\"Title of Chart\")\n",
    "    for name in playerlist:\n",
    "        plt.plot(Games[Pdict[name]], c='Black', ls='--', marker='s', ms=7, label=name)\n",
    "    plt.legend(loc = 'upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))\n",
    "    plt.xticks(list(range(scount)), Seasons[begin:end], rotation = 'vertical', color = 'white')\n",

    "    Markers = {\"KobeBryant\":'s',\"JoeJohnson\":'o',\"LeBronJames\":'^',\"CarmeloAnthony\":'D',\"DwightHoward\":'s',\"ChrisBosh\":'o',\"ChrisPaul\":'^',\"KevinDurant\":'D',\"DerrickRose\":'s',\"DwayneWade\":'o'}\n",
    "    Col  = {\"KobeBryant\":'Black',\"JoeJohnson\":'Red',\"LeBronJames\":'Green',\"CarmeloAnthony\":'Blue',\"DwightHoward\":'Magenta',\"ChrisBosh\":'Black',\"ChrisPaul\":'Red',\"KevinDurant\":'Green',\"DerrickRose\":'Blue',\"DwayneWade\":'Magenta'}\n",
    "    for name in playerlist:\n",
    "        plt.plot(Games[Pdict[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Markers[name], ms=7, label=name)\n",
    "    plt.legend(loc = 'upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))\n",
    "    plt.xticks(list(range(scount)), Seasons[begin:end], rotation = 'vertical', color = 'white')\n",

   "source": [
    "def myplot(data, playerlist = Players):\n",
    "    #title prompt\n",
    "    #title = input(\"Title?\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    #yaxis prompt\n",
    "    #ylabel = input(\"Y axis title?\")\n",
    "\n",
    "    #xaxis prompt\n",
    "    #xlabel = input(\"X axis title?\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    #a = input(\"Starting Year \")\n",
    "    #b = input(\"Ending Year \")\n",
    "    a = '2005'\n",
    "    b = '2014'\n",
    "    #count of seasons to observe\n",
    "    scount = find_count(x,'2014') + 1\n",
    "    \n",
    "    Markers = {\"KobeBryant\":'s',\"JoeJohnson\":'o',\"LeBronJames\":'^',\"CarmeloAnthony\":'D',\"DwightHoward\":'s',\"ChrisBosh\":'o',\"ChrisPaul\":'^',\"KevinDurant\":'D',\"DerrickRose\":'s',\"DwayneWade\":'o'}\n",
    "    Col  = {\"KobeBryant\":'Black',\"JoeJohnson\":'Red',\"LeBronJames\":'Green',\"CarmeloAnthony\":'Blue',\"DwightHoward\":'Magenta',\"ChrisBosh\":'Black',\"ChrisPaul\":'Red',\"KevinDurant\":'Green',\"DerrickRose\":'Blue',\"DwayneWade\":'Magenta'}\n",
    "    for name in playerlist:\n",
    "        plt.plot(data[Pdict[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Markers[name], ms=7, label=name)\n",
    "    plt.legend(loc = 'upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))\n",
    "    plt.xticks(list(range(scount)), Seasons[begin:end], rotation = 'vertical', color = 'white')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(xlabel, color = 'white', fontsize = '16')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(ylabel, rotation = 'horizontal',labelpad = 70 , fontsize = '16')\n",
    "    plt.title(title, color = 'white', fontsize = '24')\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]
  },
